      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Massgrave is a grey area, for sure, but let&amp;rsquo;s be real. &lt;em&gt;Nobody&lt;/em&gt; likes Windows, and even fewer likes paying for it. Enter the Massgrave.&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;Pirate Flag&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;160&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;160&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png&#34;&#xA;    srcset=&#34;https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png 800w, https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png 1280w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 65vw&#34;&#xA;    data-zoom-src=&#34;https://deef.dev/img/pirate-flag.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Howto&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;howto&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#howto&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Copy and paste the code below into your PowerShell terminal:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;irm &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;https&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;//&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;py&#34;&gt;activated&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;py&#34;&gt;win&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Follow the prompts and the script will take care of the rest.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
